    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a joy to drive and is in really solid shape\u2014it's super reliable and ready to hit the road with you today! I've taken great care of it, so the interior is nice and clean, and it runs beautifully. It's the perfect ride for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that's been well-loved. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
