    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior paint retains a high gloss, showing only the lightest signs of careful use, while the body panels remain straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and well-preserved; the upholstery is supple, the carpets are free of stains, and every feature\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the ice-cold air conditioning\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car has been maintained with an open checkbook policy, including recent oil services, a comprehensive multi-point inspection, and tires with deep tread remaining. It delivers a smooth, quiet ride that inspires confidence on both city streets and long highway hauls. This is a non-smoker vehicle that has been garage-kept, providing the next owner with a turnkey experience and peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
